NOTE ON SCOPE

This MIT licence covers the source code in this repository only.

* Model weights are NOT distributed here. LLaVA-1.5 / LLaVA-1.6, InstructBLIP,
  Qwen-VL-Chat, CLIP, and Grounding-DINO each remain under their own upstream
  licences; obtain them from their original providers (see
  scripts/download_weights.py).
* The HalluProbe-VL annotations in data/halluprobe_vl/ are derived from MS-COCO
  and Visual Genome and remain subject to those datasets' original terms. No
  images are redistributed here — only probe questions, labels, and relative
  image references.
